{"tid":1171581,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9 GAY佬69 船P，金鐘樣勿入","createTime":"2019-05-25T20:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T10:31:08.000Z","uid":237096,"like":11,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97353abb6cad9961cd20d3b4ece3f0c25fd5676d","tid":1171581,"uid":237096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:54:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的，6月9號星期日，我唔去浦了。夜晚出海。 我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻 Adela , 租的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwB5ewG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwB5ewG.png&h=cd9e696a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9i65ewG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9i65ewG.png&h=86b809e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐50人的，長80幾呎。 <br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的 Princess V62 坐20人 西班牙式遊艇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Nmdoqv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Nmdoqv.png&h=0c3ce37f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YQUa95w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYQUa95w.png&h=1635b6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTNj3qx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTNj3qx.png&h=a9c84625&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwZB5DS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwZB5DS.png&h=de45aa14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V7Hv95y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV7Hv95y.png&h=ee4728f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，寫意d。 <br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船。 <br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多酒。 <br />\n<br />\n星期日 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n入場費<br />\n靚仔：免費<br />\n中上樣：$200<br />\n金鐘樣：$1000<br />\n女仔：唔比去<br />\n<br />\n來吧靚仔，識d俾得起$1000去船河的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求69大家玩69，大家開開心心玩返日。"},{"pid":"d8525bbfe03f4d3da2f6e49ca2e76df9c88638f1","tid":1171581,"uid":237096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc